text: Milad Salehpour (born on January 3, 1991 in Tehran) is a Television presenter from Iran. Milad Salehpour is the host of Khush Namak on IRIB Nasim. == References == == Other websites == * * Khush Namak on IRIB Nasim Category:People from Tehran Category:Living people Category:1991 births
